casebody.data:
RECONSIDERATION OF PRIOR DECISIONS

2001-1709. Kemper v. Michigan Millers Mut. Ins. Co.

Certified State Law Question, No. 3:00CVO7799. Reported at 98 Ohio St.3d 162, 2002-Ohio-7101, 781 N.E.2d 196. On motion for reconsideration. The motion fails for want of four votes on the following vote:

Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., vote no. Moyer, C.J., Lundberg Stratton and O’Connor, JJ., vote yes. Cook, J., not participating.
